{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WebSockets","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/WebSockets","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>WebSocket</em> 是允許<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Server\">伺服器</a>與用戶端之間發起持續性的 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/TCP\">TCP <small>(en-US)</small></a> 連接，以便隨時交換資料的<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Protocol\">協定</a>。</p>\n<p>任何用戶端與伺服器端程式都能使用 WebSocket，不過一般來說，大都是在<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Browser\">網路瀏覽器</a>與伺服器之間發起的。伺服器藉由 WebSocket 可以在用戶端沒有事先請求的情況下，將數據傳遞給用戶端，以便動態更新資料。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"深入理解","title":"深入理解","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"一般常識","title":"一般常識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>維基百科的 <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Websocket\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Websocket</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技術參考","title":"技術參考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/WebSocket\">MDN 的 WebSocket 參考</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"學習之","title":"學習之","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/WebSockets_API/Writing_WebSocket_client_applications\">製作 WebSocket 客戶端應用程式</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSockets_API/Writing_WebSocket_servers\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">製作 WebSocket 伺服器 (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"深入理解","id":"深入理解"}],"summary":"WebSocket 是允許伺服器與用戶端之間發起持續性的 TCP (en-US) 連接，以便隨時交換資料的協定。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WebSockets","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WebSockets","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"WebSockets","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WebSockets","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"ti